{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "main_9", "eventName": "風暴瞭望", "entryType": "MAINLINE", "storyCode": "9-6", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "深池", "storyInfo": "上校感謝號角等人幫他找到了支持深池的渣滓，並為了找出蔓德拉等人，對塔拉人聚居處進行無差別武力威懾。氣氛緊繃之時，宴會廳突然遭遇炸彈襲擊。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_manorindoor", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$nervous_intro", "key": "$nervous_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  上校。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_227_1", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我們又見面了，斯卡曼德羅斯。", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_227_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  您似乎一點都不意外。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_227_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  意外？", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  不，從見到你的第一面起，我就一點都不意外——你註定了會和這群渣滓廝混到一起，就因為你那從貴族禮儀課裡學來的廉價同情心。", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_227_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......你跟蹤了我們？！", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_227_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我更願意把這稱為合理管控。", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  無論如何，我還是要感謝你們。要不是有你們帶路，我還找不到這麼好的機會把這些蛀蟲一網打盡。", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_227_1", "fadetime": 0.7}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  你們平時藏得還挺深的，不是嗎？", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我倒是挺好奇，是什麼讓你們膽大到就這麼聚在一起，莫非先前幾次微不足道的偷襲成果，讓你們誤以為小丘郡已經在你們的掌控下了？", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_227_1", "name2": "avg_npc_177", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  咳，咳咳......上校先生，我想這其中一定有什麼誤會。", "name": "野心勃勃的男爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_227_1", "name2": "avg_npc_177", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  波頓男爵，你說錯了，我們之間一點誤會都沒有。我對你們私底下的勾當一清二楚。", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_227_1", "name2": "avg_npc_177", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  今天在這裡聚會的只是我的一些親朋，我可以拿我自己的名譽擔保——", "name": "野心勃勃的男爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_227_1", "name2": "avg_npc_177", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  請閉嘴吧，爵士閣下。你們從祖輩那裡繼承而來的榮譽在我眼中一文不值。", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_175"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  你、你竟敢這麼說！", "name": "附庸風雅的女貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_175"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_227_1", "name2": "avg_npc_177", "fadetime": 0.7}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_227_1", "name2": "avg_npc_177", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  辱沒你們這些所謂的貴族名聲的可不是我。是誰享受著維多利亞給予的地位與財富，又在暗地裡與最下流的反叛者勾結？", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_227_1", "name2": "avg_npc_175", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  這都是徹頭徹尾的汙衊！", "name": "附庸風雅的女貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_175"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_227_1"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我開始對這些廢話感到厭倦了。渣滓就該和外面的渣滓一樣，一邊在火光裡痛哭流涕一邊為自己犯過的錯懺悔。", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就像他說的那樣，窗外傳來陣陣哭喊聲，玻璃上映出星星點點的火光。"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5", "name2": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  （隊長，你看外面！不光這裡，他把塔拉人的街區整個包圍了。）", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  （他一點都沒有誇張，他在武力威懾普通居民。）", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  （我去過那街道，他們中的很大一部分都是老人和孩子！）", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5", "name2": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  （手段突然這麼激進，看來他還掌握了別的資訊。他很可能對我們隱瞞了鬼魂部隊的情報。）", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7", "name2": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  （三角鐵沒有消息嗎？）", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7", "name2": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  （從下午起，一直沒有通訊。）", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  （糟了，他們會不會出事？）", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  （擔心也沒有意義。眼前更要緊的是，我們應該儘量阻止駐軍。）", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#6", "name2": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  （至少不能困在這裡......）", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#6"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_227_1"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  那個瓦伊凡，你可別想著破牆出去。在我問出結果之前，這間屋子裡一個人都不能走。", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......唉，被發現了啊！", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "21_G6_decisivebattlealley_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_241"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  出來！我看到你了，不許動，給我老老實實跪在這裡！", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_241"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_243"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  啊！", "name": "悲傷的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_243"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_243", "name2": "avg_npc_241", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  你家裡還有人嗎？快說！", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_241"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_243", "name2": "avg_npc_241", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  沒、沒有......", "name": "悲傷的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_243"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_243", "name2": "avg_npc_241", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  真的沒藏人？我去看一眼。聽著，只要我看到你動一下，不管你是想幹什麼，我都會立馬把你腦袋射個對穿。", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_241"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_243", "name2": "avg_npc_241", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  嗚嗚......", "name": "悲傷的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_243"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 0.9}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#6$1", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  你在做什麼啊？！", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#6$1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_241"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  誰啊，突然冒出來，還往我的弩跟前撞？小心你的腦袋！", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_241"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  咦，等一下，我認識你。你是亞當斯隊裡那個儀仗兵，對吧？我在新年活動上見過你。你們小隊沒收到行動命令吧，你在這裡幹什麼？", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_241"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我、我......", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#5$1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我在附近有別的任務要做。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#5$1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_241"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "   那行，各做各的。你可別來妨礙我。", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_241"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#9$1"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（那個叫風笛的姑娘說，我也能站出來，去改變局面。）", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#2$1"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（我可以嗎......？至少，我該試試......）", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#2$1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們......做錯了什麼，要被這麼粗暴地對待？", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#6$1"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_241"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "   你問我？你怎麼不問問他們？", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_241"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_243"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 嗚......", "name": "悲傷的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_243"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_241"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  哭什麼？窩藏暴徒，給他們送吃送喝，幫他們通風報信的不是你們嗎？", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_241"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  你有證據嗎？", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#6$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_241"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "   證據？你問我要什麼證據？九隊和十三隊的人還沒冷掉的屍體上的傷口算不算？", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_241"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  他們有的人死於恐怖的源石技藝，有的死於和我們手裡拿著的一模一樣的制式弓弩和長刀，還有的脖子上留著農用器械留下的痕跡。", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_241"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  你想過我們的腦袋像麥子一樣被割麥機切下來、身體被拖拉機碾得像剛犁過的地一樣又薄又平......的慘狀嗎？", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_241"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  呃唔......", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#9$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_241"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "   想吐就對了。我親眼看到了，我還認識那顆腦袋之前的主人，我吐了整整一個下午。", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_241"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 他們......為什麼要這樣對待同胞......這太殘忍了！", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#9$1"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_241"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈，你說對了，他們從來不配做人。", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_241"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_241"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在你明白這群人活該了吧？", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_241"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " ......", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#9$1"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_241"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還愣著幹什麼？", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_241"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 所以......這群人都是壞人嗎？就因為......他們都是塔拉人？", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#9$1"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_243"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  嗚......啊......我什麼都沒做過，長官......", "name": "悲傷的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_243"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " ......她在哭。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#9$1"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 她的丈夫已經因礦石病去世，她的孩子還只有十來歲......這樣孤苦無依的人，真的會是兇手嗎？", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#9$1"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_241"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我怎麼就跟你說不明白！他們都是一類人，你懂嗎？即便這個女人和她的小孩還沒有犯錯，他們都是一起的。", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_241"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " ......", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#9$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 如果在你們面前的，不是塔拉人，而是其他維多利亞公民......", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#8$1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 你還會堅持把他們都視作暴徒嗎？", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#6$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_241"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_241"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 如果......我是說如果，打從一開始，就沒有那些歧視性的法案，塔拉人能和其他人賺到一樣多的鑄幣，獲得一樣的醫療機會......", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#9$1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 是不是，接下來的衝突都不會發生？！", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#9$1"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_241"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "行吧，儀仗兵，你愛問問題你就問。不會有答案的，誰都沒法告訴你答案。反正這家搜得差不多了，我該去下一戶了。", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_241"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_241"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘿！我說我要走了，可沒說你能站起來！", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_241"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_243"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  嗚......啊......別抓我，克雷格不能沒有我......", "name": "悲傷的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_243"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_241"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哭哭啼啼的煩死人了！一天到晚念叨著孩子，不就是想讓我心軟嗎？", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_241"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " ......你就放過她吧。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#9$1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_241"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎，你呀，算了，看在我很忙的份上，我可以不管這個女人。", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_241"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只不過，現在你這麼好心護著他們，小心回頭他們就眼睛都不眨地轟一下把你炸上天。", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_241"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  畢竟你別忘了，你和他們不是一類人。你看過他們的眼神了嗎？在他們眼裡，無論你怎麼表現，你始終都是我們的人。", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_241"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......快走吧，求你了。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#9$1"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_241"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  嘖，別怪我沒提醒過你。", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_241"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "delay", "attributes"