的青年"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 395, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_231"}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "move", "fadetime": 0.8, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "move", "ypos": 8.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_242"}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您竟然向我伸出了手......我......", "name": "受傷的青年"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 401, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_231"}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......不會有人像剛才那樣壓迫你了。", "name": "“領袖”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_231"}, {"id": 403, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_231"}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你也不再需要任何人的攙扶。", "name": "“領袖”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_231"}, {"id": 405, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_231"}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從今往後，你可以靠自己自由地行走在這片土地上。", "name": "“領袖”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_231"}, {"id": 407, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_242"}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝......謝謝您！我做的事，果然都是正確的！", "name": "受傷的青年"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 409, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_242"}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們塔拉人......終有一天能擁有自己的城市，我們能在街道上昂首挺胸，再也不會受到任何不公正的待遇！", "name": "受傷的青年"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 411, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_231"}}, {"id": 412, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，我們正是為了這一天而來。", "name": "“領袖”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_231"}, {"id": 413, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_242"}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "領袖，快看啊，那、那是我們為您點燃的火！", "name": "受傷的青年"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 415, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_231"}}, {"id": 416, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "宴會廳......", "name": "“領袖”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_231"}, {"id": 417, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_244"}}, {"id": 418, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "按照蔓德拉女士給的情報，現在駐軍高層都在那裡。", "name": "深池士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_244"}, {"id": 419, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_244"}}, {"id": 420, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，光是這種規模的爆炸，只能挫一下駐軍的氣焰，恐怕並不能消滅他們。", "name": "深池士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_244"}, {"id": 421, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_231"}}, {"id": 422, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "除了駐軍，還有誰？", "name": "“領袖”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_231"}, {"id": 423, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_244"}}, {"id": 424, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一些向我們示好的當地人。他們知道了一些我們的底細，頭領們的意思是，為了大局，不能留活口。", "name": "深池士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_244"}, {"id": 425, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_231"}}, {"id": 426, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "“領袖”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_231"}, {"id": 427, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_244"}}, {"id": 428, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們還說，如果您不動手的話，他們會自己上。", "name": "深池士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_244"}, {"id": 429, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_231"}}, {"id": 430, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......還是我的火......更快一些。", "name": "“領袖”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_231"}, {"id": 431, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_231"}}, {"id": 432, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "通知他們，我知道該怎麼做——", "name": "“領袖”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_231"}, {"id": 433, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_231"}}, {"id": 434, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會拿下宴會廳。", "name": "“領袖”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_231"}, {"id": 435, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_244"}}, {"id": 436, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，領袖——您的火，必將打破這強壓著我們數百年的桎梏！", "name": "深池士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_244"}, {"id": 437, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 438, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 439, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 440, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 441, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 442, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 443, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}